title: Your Todos  goes public!
post_content: Your Todos is an application that helps you keep track of your todos. You can add, delete, and edit todos.

title: Habits Builder
post_content: Habits Builder is an application that helps you build habits. You can add, delete, and edit habits.

title: Friends first
post_content: Friends first is an application that helps find individuals with the same interest as you and git to hangout with them for a day in person or video calls from all over the world . You can add, delete, and edit friends.

title: Cool Pets
post_content: Cool Pets is an application that helps you find neighbors with pets and you can hangout with them and their pets. You can add, delete, and edit pets.

title: Speed Trainer
post_content: Speed Trainer is an application that helps you train your typing speed. You can add, delete, and edit words.
